# Tailwind v4 + preset policy

Preset source of truth (read-only):
- design-sytem-svelte-components/tailwind-presets/v4/theme.css

Parent repo may:
- add local theme tokens via @theme in src/app.css
- add local @layer components/utilities only in src/app.css or src/ styles
- adjust Tailwind tooling config in parent (postcss/vite) without touching submodule

Never:
- edit anything inside design-sytem-svelte-components/** (submodule)
